Department of Justice 1301 Clay Street, Room 380-N Immigration and Naturalization Service Oakland CA 94612-5217 ACCOUNTING ANA MORONTA File No.: A12797485 18998 CARLTON AVENUE Date: October 1, 1999 CASTRO VALLEY, CA. 94546 Officer: T. McBride CC: Examination of your application (N400) shows that additional information, documents or forms are needed before your application can be acted upon. Please RETURN THIS LETTER WITH REQUESTED INFORMATION and/or DOCUMENTATION by: ** see below * Failure to do so may result in the denial of your application. Please come by our office and complete an affidavit regarding your being fingerprint exempt. It would be best to come by on October 6, 13, or 18th. Some waiting may be necessary, as I have interviews scheduled for all days. These dates however should not be as much of a problem. DOT SFR Ana Dolores Moronta Winner Due to heavy workloads, please allow a minimum of three months past the due date noted above for a response. s:\forms.wrd\online\N14blank.doc OKL 12/12/97 Form N-14 (Rev. 9/16/97)N
